text:
I had a great time hanging out the
other day. I'm sending you a gift
I wasn't able to give you then.
I hope you enjoy it. And feel free
to stop by for a workout sometime.
My gym is always open!

It was so cool when you came by to
visit me the other day. I'm so sorry
that I didn't make you a protein
shake! Oh well. Maybe next time.

It was so fun when you came over
the other day. You know, sometimes
I think I should just turn my home
into a gym and recruit some
workouters. Worker outers?
Workoutees? I really like friends.
